race.description: The Chappy Plate - Fast/Fun & Far From Done Mdn Hcp
race.comment: BROKEN IMAGE (4) finds the maiden win elusive but does have four minor placings to her name. Failed to live up to market expectations when resuming at Wagga but this is easier and she's sure to have come on from that. LAUNCH MODE (7) hit the frame two starts ago at Wagga but ran below par last time over the mile. Better placed dropping back to this trip and carries a feather with the 3kg claimer engaged. Bold showing anticipated. SPEED OF GOLD (2) struggles to break through but looks to have found his best chance yet. Heywood takes over the reins. Live chance to get off the mark in a thin contest. BALLANDELLA STREET (6) and PARALIA (10) are struggling to break through but come into the mix in a race lacking quality.
